data.description: Welcome to the elegant Gated Community of Countryside Estates. This semi-custom home is move-in ready with a landscaped exterior. Inside, discover a formal Dining Room, upgraded lighting, plantation shutters, and a soothing color palette. The great room features a coffered ceiling and large windows, while the basement boasts a wet bar, 2 bedrooms, and a bathroom. The gourmet kitchen includes granite countertops, SS/black appliances, and ample upgraded wood cabinetry. The backyard offers a pool, spa, covered patio, BBQ, and palm trees. Additional features comprise under-cabinet lighting, new kitchen appliances, and a spacious master suite. Contact us today to explore this impressive home.
